Role.Description: This role will enable IT to view messages and other data issues
Role.Name: Script Tool Viewer Role

Role.Description: This role will enable IT to fix messages and other data issues using Guidewires scripting language, which is preferred over changing the database directly. Each time the tool is used an audit record is created in the database including: the date, the user who ran the script, an associated ticket number, comments, the script itself, and an XML representation of the before and after values of any changed data. A notification email is also sent to a distribution configurable via a Script Parameter.
Role.Name: Script Tool User Role
